>
  <p>Imaging Uganda/Africa is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect and use information when you visit our website.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it, for example through email communication or contact forms.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>When information is provided to us, we use it to respond to inquiries, improve our website, and share relevant updates.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use third-party services such as Google AdSense to display ads. These services may collect non-personal information such as cookies or IP addresses to deliver relevant advertising.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Cookies may be used to enhance your browsing experience and support analytics or advertising services. You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:alexmradiology@gmail.com">alexmradiology@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
